ProductDescription.LongDesc: The Panasonic UG-3350 toner cartridge ensures your fax printer will continue to deliver optimal performance and operate at ideal levels throughout its lifespan. Compatible with the UF-585 and UF-595 Laser Fax Series, this cartridge boasts a printhead duty cycle of up to 7,500 pages.\n\nUsing high-end Panasonic consumables and supplies provides sharp, high-quality output, every time. The Panasonic printers and fax-machines have been engineered to work together with their custom-designed consumables and supplies to guarantee that your document and graphical printouts are clear and sharp, every time you print. Buy authentic Panasonic products with confidence: Panasonic backs this product with a 100 percent satisfaction guarantee.
